Returns a description of the plan that is generated by the assembler and_also of the arguments if they are available. The description should be simple_text as it may be rendered in different environments (console, web interface, ...)._Typical things that should be included are:_
    _
  • expected input format
    • _
  • description of output
    • _
  • description of what is done
    • _
  • description of arguments to customize plan if available
    • _
__@return A description of the program and of its arguments if available.
